data.text:
Jeffrey Dean Morgan played Denny Duquette, Jr. in seasons two, three, and five of Grey's Anatomy.

Biography[]

He has been in a relationship with fellow actor Hilarie Burton, who played Lauren Boswell, since 2009.[source?] They have two children together[1] and married in October 2019.[2]
